~+~+duck-the-virus+~+~


~+~+~+~+~+~+
Requirements
~+~+~+~+~+~+

* python3
* A linux environment with a gui.

TO start the game

:~$ python3 -m pip install -r requirements.txt
:~$ cd src && python3 gameplay.py

~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~
How to play 
~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~

* Keys

* [up arrow] - move up

* [down-arrow]  - move down

* [left-arrow]  - move left

* [right-arrow] - move right

* [space-key] - activate shield

* [esc-key] - quit

* [pause-key] - pause for 5 seconds.

~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~

Virus and heart were taken from animatedimages.org



